name: untitled 007
description:
this is a lofi that brings me nostalgia...

I remember playing in the park with my friends on sunny days, and time always seemed to be infinite.

this song was created in collab with my friend and producer @prodFHL who also recorded the guitars and mixed it with me.

I was privileged to have the cover art designed by the wonderful @drielemart, and animated by the great @PlayManNFT.

Enjoy!
